title: TEZAI
description:
Part of the DAMzineâ€™s DAMAI project, TEZAI is an open Tezos Event dedicated to generative AI art. Mint your AI art (no worries if you work with traditional media, nobody will notice!) between 14th and 17th June (PST), using the tag "TEZAI" or "DAMAI" at mint time to be included. Deepfake it till you deepmake it!
More about DAMAI here
This event has an open gallery. Click on the "Anaver.se" button to enter it. Check this video tweet to learn how to hang a piece.
